metadata.dc:author: Oller Ariño, F
metadata.dc:description: The importance of penis/arm index, measured by means of ultrasonic Doppler, as a possible orientation in significative arterial lesions at penile level, is emphasized.
metadata.dc:title: Correlación clínica en la evaluación hemodinámica Döppler de la disfunción eréctil.
[Clinical correlation in the Doppler hemodynamic evaluation of erectile dysfunction].
